## Validation Rules (Product Endpoints)

- **Category create/update:**
  - `name`: required on create.
  - `slug`: optional, URL-friendly; auto-generated from name if omitted.
- **Product create/update:**
  - `name`: required on create.
  - `categoryId`: required on create, must reference an active category.
  - `sku`: optional, unique when provided.
- **Availability:**
